    parentName: "p"
  }, "Monitoring + alarms."), " Operating a system without monitoring is like driving at night without headlights\u2014the lack of visibility is unnerving. Detail how you\u2019ll monitor your system performance (e.g., throughput, latency, error rate, etc.) Monitoring can be done server-side (e.g., model endpoint) or client-side (e.g., consumer), with the latter including network latency. Also list the alarms that will trigger human intervention (e.g., on-call)."), mdx("p", null, mdx("strong", {
